        <div class="label">
          <h3>Store</h3>
          <p>VIP &amp; VIP+ ranks</p>
        </div>
      </a>

    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- The Collective: community server showcase -->
  <div class="collective">
    <p class="col-eyebrow">COMMUNITY SERVER · ALWAYS EVOLVING</p>
    <div class="col-head">
      <h2>The Collective</h2>
      <span class="col-live"><span class="dot"></span>Building toward 24/7</span>
    </div>
    <p class="col-vision">Alongside our major civilisation events, we're building a permanent community server to keep things active and competitive all year round. Not a lobby to wait in. A fully featured mini-event server with a growing range of game modes, refined over time. From fast-paced PvP tournaments and battle royale modes to creative challenges and social events, there's always something happening.</p>
    <div class="col-modes">
      <span class="col-mode">Hunger Games</span>
      <span class="col-mode">Survival Games</span>
      <span class="col-mode">Battle Royale</span>
      <span class="col-mode">Prop Hunt</span>
      <span class="col-mode">Random Item Challenge</span>
      <span class="col-mode">1v1 Duels</span>
      <span class="col-mode">100 Player Events</span>
    </div>
    <div class="col-rail">Progression plan</div>
    <div class="timeline">
      <div class="phase">
        <div class="node">1</div>
        <div class="ptag">WEEKS 1–2</div>
        <h4>Launch</h4>
        <p>Weekend-only events, online during scheduled sessions. We start simple with Hunger Games to build the initial community and get things running smoothly.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="phase">
        <div class="node">2</div>
        <div class="ptag">WEEKS 3–8</div>
        <h4>Expanding</h4>
        <p>Events move to Wednesday, Friday and Sunday sessions. More modes arrive gradually including Survival Games, Battle Royale, Prop Hunt, Random Item Challenge and 1v1 Duels as the schedule gets more consistent.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="phase">
        <div class="node">3</div>
        <div class="ptag">MONTH 3+</div>
        <h4>Going 24/7</h4>
        <p>Fully online 24/7 with every mode available any time. Weekly 100 player events run alongside hosted tournaments on a regular schedule, plus a planned MCPVP partnership for a cross-server duel queue.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</main>

<%- include('partials/foot') %>

<script>
document.getElementById('showMore').addEventListener('click', function() {
  var m = document.getElementById('moreText');
  var open = m.classList.toggle('open');
  this.classList.toggle('open', open);
  this.querySelector('.t').textContent = open ? 'Show less' : 'Show more';
  this.setAttribute('aria-expanded', open);
});
</script>
